{"id":307,"parent_id":302,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":307,"title":"1 Kings 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Kgs.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Solomon solicits and gains Hiram’s help in getting timber to build the temple—The Israelites hew stones and cut timber for the temple."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.1","order":"02.12.005.24257"},["b","1"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Hiram"],"king of Tyre sent his servants unto Solomon; for he had heard that they had anointed him king in the room of his father: for Hiram was ever a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"lover"],"of David."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.2","order":"02.12.005.24258"},["b","2"],"And Solomon sent to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Hiram"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.3","order":"02.12.005.24259"},["b","3"],"Thou knowest how that David my father could not build an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"house"],"unto the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"his God for the wars which were about him on every side, until the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Lord"]],"put them under the soles of his feet."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.4","order":"02.12.005.24260"},["b","4"],"But now the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God hath given me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"rest"],"on every side,",["i","so that there is"],"neither adversary nor evil occurrent."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.5","order":"02.12.005.24261"},["b","5"],"And, behold, I purpose to build an house unto the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto David my father, saying, Thy son, whom I will set upon thy throne in thy room, he shall build an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"house"],"unto my name."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.6","order":"02.12.005.24262"},["b","6"],"Now therefore command thou that they hew me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"cedar"],"trees out of Lebanon; and my servants shall be with thy servants: and unto thee will I give hire for thy servants according to all that thou shalt appoint: for thou knowest that",["i","there is"],"not among us any that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"can skill"],"to hew timber like unto the Sidonians."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.7","order":"02.12.005.24263"},["b","7"],"¶And it came to pass, when Hiram heard the words of Solomon, that he rejoiced greatly, and said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Blessed"],["i","be"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"this day, which hath given unto David a wise son over this great people."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.8","order":"02.12.005.24264"},["b","8"],"And Hiram sent to Solomon, saying, I have considered the things which thou sentest to me for:",["i","and"],"I will do all thy desire concerning timber of cedar, and concerning timber of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fir"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.9","order":"02.12.005.24265"},["b","9"],"My servants shall bring",["i","them"],"down from Lebanon unto the sea: and I will convey them by sea in floats unto the place that thou shalt appoint me, and will cause them to be discharged there, and thou shalt receive",["i","them:"],"and thou shalt accomplish my desire, in giving food for my household."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.10","order":"02.12.005.24266"},["b","10"],"So Hiram gave Solomon cedar trees and fir trees",["i","according to"],"all his desire."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.11","order":"02.12.005.24267"},["b","11"],"And Solomon gave Hiram twenty thousand measures of wheat",["i","for"],"food to his household, and twenty measures of pure oil: thus gave Solomon to Hiram year by year."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.12","order":"02.12.005.24268"},["b","12"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"gave Solomon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"wisdom"],", as he promised him: and there was peace between Hiram and Solomon; and they two made a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"league"],"together."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.13","order":"02.12.005.24269"},["b","13"],"¶And king Solomon raised a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"levy"],"out of all Israel; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"levy"],"was thirty thousand men."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.14","order":"02.12.005.24270"},["b","14"],"And he sent them to Lebanon, ten thousand a month by courses: a month they were in Lebanon,",["i","and"],"two months at home: and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Adoniram"],["i","was"],"over the levy."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.15","order":"02.12.005.24271"},["b","15"],"And Solomon had threescore and ten thousand that bare",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"burdens"],", and fourscore thousand",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"hewers in the mountains"],";"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.16","order":"02.12.005.24272"},["b","16"],"Beside the chief of Solomon’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"officers"],"which",["i","were"],"over the work, three thousand and three hundred, which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"ruled"],"over the people that wrought in the work."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.17","order":"02.12.005.24273"},["b","17"],"And the king commanded, and they brought great stones,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"costly"],"stones,",["i","and"],"hewed",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"stones"],", to lay the foundation of the house."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.18","order":"02.12.005.24274"},["b","18"],"And Solomon’s builders and Hiram’s builders did hew",["i","them,"],"and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"stonesquarers"],": so they prepared timber and stones to build the house."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.1a","order":"02.12.005.24275"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.11"},"2 Sam. 5:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.1b","order":"02.12.005.24277"},["b","1b"],"The Hebrew term here expresses the affection held by one friend for another;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.21"},"1 Sam. 16:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/18.1,3"},"18:1, 3"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.2a","order":"02.12.005.24279"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/2.3.3-16"},"2 Chr. 2:3 (3–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.3a","order":"02.12.005.24281"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.3b","order":"02.12.005.24283"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.7"},"Alma 46:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.4a","order":"02.12.005.24285"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/4.24.24-25"},"1 Kgs. 4:24 (24–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.9"},"1 Chr. 22:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.5a","order":"02.12.005.24287"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/5.16"},"2 Ne. 5:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.31"},"D&C 84:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.119.119-120"},"88:119 (119–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.12.10-17"},"97:12 (10–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.6a","order":"02.12.005.24289"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.4"},"1 Chr. 22:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/3.7"},"Ezra 3:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.10"},"2 Ne. 19:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.6b","order":"02.12.005.24291"},["b","6b"],["span.small","HEB"],"know how."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.7a","order":"02.12.005.24293"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/10.9"},"1 Kgs. 10:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.8a","order":"02.12.005.24295"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.34"},"1 Kgs. 6:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.12a","order":"02.12.005.24297"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/3.12"},"1 Kgs. 3:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.17"},"D&C 46:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.12b","order":"02.12.005.24299"},["b","12b"],["span.small","HEB"],"covenant, pact."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.13a","order":"02.12.005.24301"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/12.4"},"1 Kgs. 12:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.13b","order":"02.12.005.24303"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.15"},"1 Kgs. 9:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.14a","order":"02.12.005.24305"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/4.6"},"1 Kgs. 4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/12.18"},"12:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.15a","order":"02.12.005.24307"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.21.20-22"},"1 Kgs. 9:21 (20–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.15b","order":"02.12.005.24309"},["b","15b"],["span.small","IE"],"hewers of stone."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.16a","order":"02.12.005.24311"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/4.5"},"1 Kgs. 4:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.16b"